# Trivy misconfiguration suppressions
# Each entry is a finding ID with the rationale for accepting the risk.

# AVD-AWS-0104: Security group allows unrestricted egress
# EKS nodes must reach the internet for ECR image pulls, OS package updates,
# and the Kubernetes API. Restricting egress by destination is done at the
# NACLs / Firewall layer, not the instance security group.
AVD-AWS-0104

# AVD-AWS-0175: EKS cluster has public endpoint enabled
# Access is restricted via public_access_cidrs to the caller's CIDR.
# Fully private clusters require a bastion or VPN, which is out of scope here.
AVD-AWS-0175

# AVD-AWS-0123: RDS / Aurora minor version auto-upgrade disabled
# Minor version upgrades are applied during maintenance windows; the module
# exposes the variable and leaves the choice to each environment.
AVD-AWS-0123
